Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星地球的毁灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The destruction of planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个想法激发了无尽的预言 预测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The idea has inspired endless prophecies, predictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及科幻故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and science fiction stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们可以胡思乱想种种刺激的场景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One could imagine all kinds of exciting scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间汽化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instant vaporization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极度的拉面过程(spaghettification)\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Extreme spaghettification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物质破坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Antimatter devastation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在天王星和天文物理学领域的顶尖专家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now leading experts in the fields of astronomy and astrophysics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出各自的招术来摧毁地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}devise their own plots to destroy the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会看到大楼熔化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You would have buildings melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质一下子没了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Matter would turn into goo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠重力维系的一切分崩瓦解了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything that's held together by gravity would disintegrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种爆炸式方式来揭示我们地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an explosive way to uncover the extreme science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宇宙的极端科学\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of our planet and the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看地球终结的10个景象 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get set for 10 visions of terrestrial termination:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十大毁灭地球之招\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"10 Ways to Destroy the Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别随便尝试 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't try this at home.
