Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.18,0:38:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十大摧毁地球之招的名录上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On the list of 10 ways to destroy the Earth,
