Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.08,0:40:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会变成这种黏糊糊的夸克汤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would turn into just this goo, this soup of quarks.
