Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力的消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the end of gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.44,0:40:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物质以及怪异物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}antimatter and strange matter.
