Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 天体物理学家菲耶尔 奥泽尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, astrophysicist Feryal Ozel
