Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.76,0:41:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就会把我们带到另一种形态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This would just take us into another state.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.97,0:41:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是毁灭地球第1招 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the number 1 way to destroy the Earth:
