Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.15,0:41:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在着其它宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the existence of other universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.83,0:41:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准其他宇宙中存在着地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's possible that there are Earths in other universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们的宇宙想象为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Think of our universe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二维的薄片 存在于这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a two-dimensional sheet, which exists here,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动在薄片里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and moving around in the sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.05,0:41:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是活动在我们的三维空间里一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is like moving around in our three spatial dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.43,0:41:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你可以朝这另一个方向移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But then you can move in this other direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.22,0:42:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要出薄片了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is sort of off the sheet,
