Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.72,0:42:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将是个不同的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that would be a different universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.60,0:42:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宇宙或许就像那个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our universe would be just like that one perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.39,0:42:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许少有不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or maybe slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.44,0:42:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是极其重要的要意识到 我们不能让\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it's very important to realize that we shouldn't have
