Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.78,0:42:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设想我们的宇宙是一张纸 如这个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine that our universe is a piece of paper, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.87,0:42:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后附近的宇宙将会是这张纸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then a nearby universe would be this piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.41,0:42:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在假如这两张纸碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now if the two pieces of paper were to collide,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.37,0:42:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以听到那能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you can hear that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.87,0:42:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来想象两张宇宙般大小的纸相碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now imagine two sheets of paper the size of the universe colliding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.92,0:42:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有多少能量在那样的碰撞中泄漏出来？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How much energy would be imparted at a collision like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.72,0:42:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们不知怎么的接触到了一个平行宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we somehow did make contact with a parallel universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.47,0:42:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将会是我们所知的最后的事情了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it could be the last thing we'd ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.52,0:42:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将不仅是毁灭行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would not just destroy planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.40,0:42:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会毁灭太阳系 星系 星系团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would destroy solar systems, galaxies, clusters of galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.53,0:42:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会毁灭一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.61,0:43:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会是这个现存宇宙的终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be the end of this current universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.41,0:43:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是万物的终结会不会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But is it possible that the end of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.00,0:43:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是其它万物的开端呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the beginning of everything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.71,0:43:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一个大爆炸创造了我们的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If one Big Bang created our universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.59,0:43:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么另一个大爆炸会重新开始整个事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then another Big Bang could start the whole thing over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有可能创造另一个宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It might create another universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.94,0:43:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这最不可思议的末日情景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And maybe this most incredible of doomsday scenarios
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.94,0:43:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯一一个已经发生过的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the only one that's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.57,0:43:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爆炸说不定来自这样一对宇宙的碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Big Bang came from the collision of such a pair of universes perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.37,0:43:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此没准会再次发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So maybe it's going to happen again.
