Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.42,0:43:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经过100亿年 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then after about 10 billion years 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.13,0:44:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许在另一个宇宙间存在着另一个地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe there would be another Earth in another universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.14,0:44:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到了地球毁灭于突然撞击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've seen the Earth destroyed by sudden impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.64,0:44:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严寒 酷热\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}bitter cold, and vaporizing heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.65,0:44:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它停止了自旋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's been stopped in its rotation,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.32,0:44:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被怪异物质转换\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}transformed by strange matter,
